VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \binsecureHTTPParser\s*:\s*true\b
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:insecureHTTPParser:\s*true|legacyHeaders:\s*true && MISSING:test|development|legacy
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects explicit enablement of Node's insecure HTTP parser option.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Insecure HTTP Parser Enabled.
